%% 3.2.19 Receive Push Notifications — sequence
%% Firebase FCM — DeviceToken stored on User (send on Login)
%% BR51: High-priority delivery for boarding / alighting safety alerts

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Driver as Driver or Teacher App
    participant BE as Backend (Attendance / Notification)
    participant FCM as Firebase FCM
    participant App as Guardian Mobile
    actor Guardian as Guardian

    Driver->>BE: Student check-in event
    BE->>BE: Resolve guardian DeviceToken
